---
title: Mediterranean Tender Beef & Cheesy Risoni Stew with Pre-Cut Veggies & Parsley
description: We love a slow cooker dish - add all your ingredients and come back later to a meal that is sure to be warm, hearty and
comforting. This one involves a rich beef ragu with risoni to keep you satisfied. We can’t wait to dig in!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6711cc1f96339e2a0bba13f0-12ab1655.jpeg
